{"tid":538492,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"去年第4季IPHONE X全球出貨2,900萬 中國占700萬","createTime":"2018-01-23T16:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T15:01:22.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7756c9fb365d057a450c30b0d688eb0bd77f918a","tid":538492,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"華爾街見聞報導，調研公司Canalys發布報告稱，2017年第4季度iPhone X全球出貨2,900萬支，是該季度出貨量最高的智慧手機，其中，中國市場占了700萬支。<br />\n<br />\n除了iPhone X，iPhone SE、iPhone 6s、iPhone 7等舊機型在2017年第4季度的表現也相當不錯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApple已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998d550a914569c8ae2212101981694409211c4c","tid":538492,"uid":81397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"果d估iphone x總銷量1800萬既分析師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183a279ae05e9b498a050f1b59e05b583e94e684","tid":538492,"uid":33483,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:06:07.000Z","msg":"支你老母閪咩"},{"pid":"92799cd487847e2f66a80584c12612ec76de2607","tid":538492,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"Canalys: Apple&rsquo;s iPhone X shipped 29 million in Q4, &lsquo;slightly below industry expectations&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\nAs the debate over sales of Apple&rsquo;s iPhone X continues to brew, a research firm released data today that&rsquo;s sure to provoke another round of thumb-sucking.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to Canalys, Apple shipped 29 million iPhone Xs in Q4 2017 (a quarter Apple would refer to as Q1 2018), making the device the &ldquo;world&rsquo;s best-shipping smartphone model over the holiday season.&rdquo; Given a price tag that starts at $999 and the fact that it was only available in limited supplies for just over half the quarter, that would seem like a huge success.<br />\n<br />\nBut&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The iPhone X performance is impressive for a device priced at US$999, but it is slightly below industry expectations,&rdquo; said Canalys analyst Ben Stanton, in a statement.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Apple is dying"},{"pid":"24b498f95c88918c8bd81ee5c07d54eabf5d2f83","tid":538492,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:17:22.000Z","msg":"iPhone X稱霸全球　2個月狂賣2900萬支<br />\n2018/01/24 00:01<br />\n研究業者canalys昨在最新報告中指出，2017年第4季蘋果iPhone X出貨量達到2900萬支，其中中國貢獻700萬支，iPhone X是年終假期購物季出貨量最高的智慧手機。<br />\ncanalys分析師史坦頓（Ben Stanton）說：「從999美元的價格來看，iPhone X表現令人印象深刻，但iPhone X表現略低於業界預期。」<br />\n史坦頓表示，去年11月初蘋果飽受供給問題所苦，但去年11月底及12月iPhone X產量大增，這有助於iPhone X產量在上季結束前滿足甚至超越部分市場需求。不過，史坦頓也指出，iPhone X價格高昂和蘋果訂出不同上市時間的策略仍產生影響，iPhone X出貨量未改寫iPhone問世以來最高紀錄。<br />\niPhone SE、6s、7和8機型去年第4季出貨量表現也很好，這些手機仍受尋找價格合理產品的iPhone用戶歡迎。canalys分析師阮同安（音譯）說：「拜蘋果去年第3季大幅調整產品組合之賜，蘋果將寫下史上最佳表現。」<br />\niPhone X於去年11月3日開賣，iPhone 8和iPhone 8 Plus則在去年9月22日上市。（林文彬／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c089884b58c2b751c8da966c9f3744ce22368669","tid":538492,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:17:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180124/1284467/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180124%2F1284467%2F&d=VAXC2xZ5z49rwWZLmhwaqNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=203aa9dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180124%2F1284467%2F&h=b7e4b1ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180124/1284467/</a>"},{"pid":"e09616d78c4b275164e869b10bf13f1c8c020833","ti